  "description": "<p>继微软在亚马逊上试水Xbox One手柄预定之后，现在，这家公司终于开放了自己的预售渠道。目前，消费者可以在微软官网上预定Xbox One手柄、耳机、充电器等配件。其中，无线版手柄已经接受预定，其预定价格为59.99美元，跟早前亚马逊的预定价格一样。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2f3e3933/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F246281.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E5%BC%80%E6%94%BEXbox+One%E6%89%8B%E6%9F%84%E5%8F%8A%E8%80%B3%E6%9C%BA%E9%A2%84%E5%94%AE%E6%B8%A0%E9%81%93\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F246281.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E5%BC%80%E6%94%BEXbox+One%E6%89%8B%E6%9F%84%E5%8F%8A%E8%80%B3%E6%9C%BA%E9%A2%84%E5%94%AE%E6%B8%A0%E9%81%93\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F246281.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E5%BC%80%E6%94%BEXbox+One%E6%89%8B%E6%9F%84%E5%8F%8A%E8%80%B3%E6%9C%BA%E9%A2%84%E5%94%AE%E6%B8%A0%E9%81%93\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F246281.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E5%BC%80%E6%94%BEXbox+One%E6%89%8B%E6%9F%84%E5%8F%8A%E8%80%B3%E6%9C%BA%E9%A2%84%E5%94%AE%E6%B8%A0%E9%81%93\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F246281.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E5%BC%80%E6%94%BEXbox+One%E6%89%8B%E6%9F%84%E5%8F%8A%E8%80%B3%E6%9C%BA%E9%A2%84%E5%94%AE%E6%B8%A0%E9%81%93\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" s